#OtterZ set up a battle with 𝑛
 monsters in order to increase his combat power. Each monster has a combat power 𝑎𝑖
 and OtterZ has a combat power of 𝑐
. He has 𝑘
 flip flops and can perform the following operations:

Kill an alive monster 𝑖
 if 𝑎𝑖≤𝑐
; then 𝑐
 becomes 𝑐+𝑎𝑖
.
Throw a flip flop at an alive monster 𝑖
; the flip-flop will be broken and the monster will become angrier, then 𝑎𝑖
 becomes 𝑎𝑖+1
.
Help OtterZ obtain the maximum possible 𝑐
 after the battle.

def flipflop(L,c,k):
    t=0
    for i in range(len(L)):
     if L[i]<c:
        t=1
        if k>c-L[i]:
            c=2*c
            k=k-c+L[i]
        else:
            c=c+L[i]+k
            k=0
        L.pop(i)
        flipflop(L,c,k)
        break
     
    for i in range(len(L)):
        if L[i]==c:
            t=1
            c=c+L[i]
            L.pop(i)
            flipflop(L,c,k)
            break
     
     
    if t==0:
        return c
print(flipflop([14,9,11],6,3))
